<h3>Q:</h3>Can it edit Netflix?
<br/>
<h3>A:</h3>Well...we decided not to include that functionality because it seemed like it violated parts of their Terms of Use ("no injection of code" it says).  Feel free to contact their support and tell them you wish you could use plugins that "don't violate copyright" to help with your playback :) We hope to eventually support Netflix, even if it requires massive work arounds.  For now we will recommend to our users that they purchase their streamed media from other sources :)
